{"tid":2120304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近分左手 現實搵唔到人講只好上嚟連登懺悔下順便勸吓世","createTime":"2020-07-22T15:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T09:49:05.000Z","uid":88104,"like":18,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e83b350a89dfcc5ecc989ccd2b17919d4408646e","tid":2120304,"uid":88104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"之前拎左EX個連登AC 取消左自己追蹤<br />\n所以佢應該都見唔到<br />\n其實佢對我真係幾好<br />\n我自己都真係好鍾意佢<br />\n亦都FEEL到佢真係好鍾意我<br />\n但係可能因為上一段感情<br />\n唔敢亦都唔太識表達自已<br />\n做到好似對佢好差咁<br />\n之前聽佢講佢同我拍左2年拖<br />\n一直都諗緊我係咪鐘意佢<br />\n我呆撚左<br />\n先知我一直以後都係咁<br />\n明明愛佢但係做出嚟同我諗唔同<br />\n對唔住呀 雖然佢已經見唔到<br />\n最後勸勸大家對女朋友好啲<br />\n唔好好似我咁 搞到女朋友都冇咗<br />\n我真係好撚柒弱智<br />\n如果有時光機就好<br />\n其實分左手 佢如果開心咗<br />\n我都冇咩好講<br />\n你份新工要加油呀<br />\n我愛你呀:&lt;"},{"pid":"552bfbad966f39ce72d33a639c020a7d60954f47","tid":2120304,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"之前拎左EX個連登AC 取消左自己追蹤<br />\n<br />\n幫你推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768c2dca1adda2aff01f1aa3896e05ef29a77cbf","tid":2120304,"uid":31386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"你咁想俾個女仔睇到 咪幫你推下post"},{"pid":"d7754109d84ebd7b311325f63f6cae07b5dce428","tid":2120304,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"552bfbad966f39ce72d33a639c020a7d60954f47","tid":2120304,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"之前拎左EX個連登AC 取消左自己追蹤<br />\n<br />\n幫你推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2271b416ec71c0addcbbab0c5fde91d741cd13ee","tid":2120304,"uid":88104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"552bfbad966f39ce72d33a639c020a7d60954f47","tid":2120304,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTi